-- Longfor Buys Land in Yantai, Shandong, at Auction for 3.42 Billion Yuan
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-26T14:57:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/longfor-buys-land-in-yantai-shandong-at-auction-for-3-42-billion-yuan.html
Longfor Properties Co. bought a 2.88
million-square-meter development site in Yantai, Shandong
pronvice for 3.42 billion yuan, the company said in a Hong Kong
stock exchange filing.  The company can build as much as 4.98 million square meters
of buildings for residential, commercial, recreational, medical
and ancillary use on the site, Longfor said today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  